<div data-tag="spoiler"><strong>Autoskill :</strong> Meteor; Blizzard; Thor Hammer; Earthquake; Nemesis; Dark Javelin; Qadal [Day based element Magic]<br /><strong>Damage :</strong> A+<br /><strong>Proc Rate :</strong> C<br /><strong>Survival :</strong> C<br /><strong>Stats :</strong> C<br /><strong>Overall :</strong> 9.0<br /><strong>Description:</strong> DEF: 0 A token of appreciation from Nixe, Magic attack chance by attack<br />Mission Reward:【King of the Sun】<strong><br />Notes:</strong> Magic attack element changes depending on the day of the week: Monday: Neutral (Qadal). Tuesday: Fire (Meteor storm). Wednesday: Water (Blizzard). Thursday: Wind (Thor Hammer). Friday: Earth ( Earthquake) &gt; (At MATK 6000, ~16000 damage). Saturday: Light (Nemesis). Sunday: Dark (Dark Javelin) &gt; (At MATK 6000, ~13000 damage). Always Slot<br /><strong>Review:</strong> Magic autoskill depending on the day (see Notes). This spec damage do low damage, however it will be different story if equipped to enchanter. With correct Origin level, this spec damage can be comparable with Dajarte, even better if you use it against appropriate mob. Another great side from this spec, this spec is MQ reward and always slot. Only use this spec during special status condition for more DPS.</div>
